  "text": "Later, in [CITATION_1] , the authors focus more formally on annotation. A general framework is described which annotates the images in a collection using relevance feedback instances. As a user browses an image database using a CBIR system, providing relevance feedback as the query progresses, the system automatically annotates images using the relationships described by the user.",
